high_descs: Enter the bedroom go near to the bed.
Take a ladle from the bed.
Turn right and go to the other side of the pan.
Place the ladle on a pan in the bed.
Take the pan along with the spoon from the bed.
Turn around to the cabinet side.
Place the pan and the spoon in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take a ladle and the pan place it in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn right to reach the bed.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Head to the middle of the pan.
Put the ladle on the right pan on the bed.
Pick up the pan from the bed.
Head to the cabinet on the right.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the ladle containing the spoon in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight and then turn right to reach the bed in the bedroom.
Take a ladle from the bed.
Turn right and again take a left turn to reach the pan.
Put the ladle on the right side tray on the bed.
Take the pan along with the spoon.
Turn towards back to reach the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, then put the pan along with the spoon inside the cabinet and then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the ladle along with the pan in the cabinet
